com.android.application

Class ConnectionsConfigurationClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.application.ConnectionsConfigurationClass
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BluetoothConfigurationClass, WirelessConfigurationClass

    public class ConnectionsConfigurationClass
extends java.lang.Object
    It stores all data collected from the server during establishing connection that application needs. It is the base class for different types of connections that are possible to establish (BluetoothConfigurationClass and WirelessConfigurationClass).

    tomasz
